## Limitations

This report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of global markets means that new developments could alter the factors influencing oil prices. Additionally, the analysis is limited to the sources accessed, which may not cover all aspects of the issue comprehensively. Further research and continuous monitoring of the situation are recommended for the most current insights.

